      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Reference is made to the memorandum from Mr. Baughman to Mr. [REDACTED] Harbo, dated August 28, 1947, requesting advice as to the final disposi- tion of material submitted by Mrs. [REDACTED] Estill, South Carolina.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "It is noted that this material, which [REDACTED] reported to be a part of a flying saucer, has been identified as powdered soap stones.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
